name: GA Property evaluation
description: Each Google Analytics account has properties that group views of the data. The properties' information needs to be evaluated to ensure that the tracking is set appropriately.

blocks.description: Prepares data and checks that there is a default view.
blocks.failMessage: There is no default view defined.

blocks.description: Checks that the website URL has defined protocol.
blocks.passMessage: All website URLs have protocol defined.
blocks.failMessage: Some website URLs has no protocol.
